u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3210,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/16\/ghusl-before-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":3213,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ghusl: Perform ritual bath before Friday prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTaking a bath on Friday is a duty upon every person who has reached the age of puberty.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 839,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 846 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15810,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/hour-dua-friday\/","url_meta":{"origin":3213,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Special hour for Friday supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, mentioned the day of Friday and he said, \u201cIn it is a moment in which no Muslim stands to pray and ask Allah for something but that he will be given it,\"\u00a0and he indicated with his hand\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-prays-after-friday-in-his-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":3213,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Friday: The Prophet prays after Friday in his house","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not pray after Friday prayer until he had departed and thus would pray in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 895, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 882 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/03\/nawafil-salat-separated\/","url_meta":{"origin":3213,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary prayers separated from obligatory prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyyah reported: When you perform the Friday prayer, do not pray another prayer until you have spoken or left the mosque. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, commanded us to do that, to not connect two prayers together unless we have spoken or we have left.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25635,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/19\/ghusl-once-seven-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":3213,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ghusl: Take a bath at least once a week","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is a duty for Allah upon every Muslim to perform a ritual bath at least once every seven days, washing his head and his body.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 856, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 849 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3213","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3213"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3213\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3213"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\